{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1967,"month":9,"day":22}],"page_start":5,"page_end":5,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"喜相逢〔快板书〕","authors":["张甲祥"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席“拥军爱民”的伟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大号召震长空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全国军民齐响应。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一天，金色的太阳当头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大路上车来人往好繁荣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只听得汽车喇叭嘀嘀叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有两辆解放牌卡车对面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两辆车都竖着毛主席的彩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"色像，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车帮上毛主席语录红彤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（白）一条是：“没"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一个人民的军队，便没"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人民的一切。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条是：“军队须和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民众打成一片，使军队在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民众眼睛中看成是自己的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军队，这个军队便无敌于"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天下”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只听得两边的锣鼓越来越"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"近声越大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俩车一错“噌”的一声各自"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔西东。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没想到，这一错车出了新"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问题，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车上的人们齐声叫喊把车"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"停。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俩司机同时听到停车令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舵轮一扭靠着路边把车"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"停。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志们要问这是怎么回"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来是亲人半路喜相逢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个车上，跳下来一位解"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他就是当地驻军某部连长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高卫东。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个车上，跳下来“工人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总部”的勤务员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这小伙子名叫王志忠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个人对面跑过来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个亲热劲儿简直没法好"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"形容。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小王说：“高连长！你们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又去执行任务？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连长说（白）：“是啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是按照伟大领袖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的战略部署去执"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行一项政治任务！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们正要去工厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给你们送‘爱民公约’走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一程。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小王说：“好啊！你们不"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愧是爱民的好模范，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发扬了解放军的老传统。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从咱伟大领袖毛主席发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出‘支左’号令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们就闻风而动坚决执"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们的支左分队到俺厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立场坚定旗帜又鲜明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺‘工人总部’有你们做"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后盾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命造反腰杆更加硬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些受蒙蔽的群众一天天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在觉醒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走资本主义道路当权派失"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去了臭威风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席发出‘拥军爱民’"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的新号令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们又坚决照办打先锋。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小王他滔滔不绝往下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高连长赶紧插话搭了声："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“哎！小王啊！你不要张"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口就表扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"希望你对俺多批评。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺连队在支左当中有啥缺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点和错误，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提出来我们好改正。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命派的工人立场坚定眼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"睛亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们永远做你们的小学"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你们，揪出了走资本主"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"义道路的当权派，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你们，挺身而出粉碎了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反革命复辟妖风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你们，坚决执行毛主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的革命路线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"誓死同一小撮坏家伙作斗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狠抓革命促生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保证了生产指标超额完"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小王说：“你别说啦！我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"们做得还不够，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有啥缺点请批评。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的‘拥军公约’刚订"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正要请你们提提意见再补"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"充。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高连长听说要把“拥军公"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"约”送，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里甭提多激动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（白）“小王同志！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“哎！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“既然咱都是登门送公"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"约，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我建议，马上就读给大家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（白）“好哇！雷厉风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高连长回过头一声令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汽车上跳下三十多个子弟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小王他回头一招手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车上的工人赶紧往下蹦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗬！你看吧！军民之间又"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是握手又是笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马路上洋溢着一片鱼水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高连长、王志忠两个人手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿“公约”队前站，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条一条念得清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个念：“坚决支持无产"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级革命派。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个读：“坚决和解放军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团结得紧又紧。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个念：“向革命派工人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个读：“向解放军同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"致敬！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个念：“高举毛泽东思"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想伟大红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在无产阶级文化大革命运"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"动中立新功。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个读：“紧跟毛主席的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大战略部署向前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远做毛主席的好工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最后，双方都表示决心："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把革命大批判推向新高"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"峰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军民一起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并肩战斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"集中目标，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"集中火力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向资产阶级司令部发起猛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷追猛打“落水狗”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不获全胜不收兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霎时间，口号声声震天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声四起绕长空。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军民齐唱《大海航行靠舵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手》，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"齐声歌颂伟大导师、伟大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领袖、伟大统帅、伟大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舵手毛主席。"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"革命大批判","type":"主题/事件"},{"name":"党内资产阶级","type":"主题/事件"},{"name":"军队支左","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}